ago to make them think theyve suceed in the reprograming but it is only  a 
fake..and it is undectable. You will have a block keeping you from being 
reprogramed. Good luck temptress." He shut the pod and punched in the 
coordinates a few miles outside the base. The pod shot off into space on the 
opposite side of the planet.
